title: Win Bobby’s Money Turns Controversial + Lauren Alaina Makes Big Life Announcement
itunes:title: Win Bobby’s Money Turns Controversial + Lauren Alaina Makes Big Life Announcement
description:
Bobby goes head-to-head against a listener named Lisa in a round of “Win Bobby’s Money,” but some controversy arises over the game questions. The show shares the celebrities who they are ‘super fans’ of. Also, Lauren Alaina stops by to talk about her single, talk to a super fan, and makes a big life announcement.
